{"tid":1785572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［聖誕節遊行集會］唔啱聽既說話你聽唔聽？","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T13:45:50.000Z","uid":142098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79e7097980dd9200c9f769b5a67db4c3a41cc099","tid":1785572,"uid":142098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"我唔反對經濟攬炒 我讚成黃色經濟圈 亦都有幫襯黃店 成效好顯著<br />\n<br />\n但我反對聖誕遊行或者集會 一黎 聖誕要人出黎遊行集會人數已經會比平時少 二黎聖誕節都可以過得好黃 真係未必要令到所有人都唔可以過到聖誕節 有啲人娛樂同社運會分得好開 玩時玩認真時認真 咁樣做反而會令一少部分人反感<br />\n<br />\n成個運動都已經半年幾 大家都有幾落力 大家都知 但如果聖誕節都要用攬炒心態黎過 sorry 我做唔到 我都需要啲放鬆既時間 我已經日日精神崩緊<br />\n<br />\n我唔係分化 我唔介意你地去遊行集會或勇武 即使個3日點我都唔會割 但建議會變成聖誕節幫襯黃店好過遊行集會 btw亦希望各手足唔好怪我唔參與集會遊行 <br />\n<br />\n利申： 成日都會發夢上前既手足<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命🇭🇰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d719d873020fb350c86469eabf393c88c967795","tid":1785572,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e11ed9b4ccc561aa3a038346ca6b4f2510a3d15e","tid":1785572,"uid":159852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓主比人插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99d78aa693f347bfd1dfb5c86e1c38c580b4419","tid":1785572,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑衫為記"},{"pid":"64ec90e04947f314b34195e67d8faec68b22bc23","tid":1785572,"uid":142098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor